==English==

===Etymology===
{{LL.}} vocabularium, vocabularius: {{F.}} vocabulaire. See [[vocable]].

===Noun===
'''vocabulary''' (''plural:'' [[vocabularies]])

#A collection of [[word]]s alphabetized; a [[dictionary]].
#The collection of [[word]]s one knows and uses.

